    <title>STL-迭代器（iterator）</title>
    <link href="http://example.com/2021/03/26/STL-%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%99%A8/"/>
    <id>http://example.com/2021/03/26/STL-%E8%BF%AD%E4%BB%A3%E5%99%A8/</id>
    <published>2021-03-25T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2021-04-01T08:50:55.295Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="stl迭代器iterator"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#stl迭代器iterator"></a> STL–迭代器（iterator）</h1><h2 id="序言"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#序言"></a> 序言</h2><p>写这系列博客的原因是因为自己想继续提升，并用好<code>STL</code>这一神器，但是gnu里的源代码过于冗杂，继承关系太多，不好跟踪，可能会导致有些像我一样对<code>STL</code>感兴趣的小伙伴会看不懂如何实现，因此开辟该系列博客，会持续更新。。。</p><div class="note warning modern"><p>特此声明：本博客中数据结构调用方法均与<code>STL</code>相同。（类<code>STL</code>实现，具有容器，迭代器，但未实现空间配置器，也不会有内存管理，只关注容器与算法。</p></div><p>我们都知道，<code>STL</code>是容器和算法分离的设计模式，而迭代器<code>iterator</code>则扮演着粘胶的角色。</p><p>迭代器（<code>iterator</code>）是一种智能指针，也就是一种行为类似指针的对象，而指针在<code>C++</code>中最重要且最常用的便是提领（<code>dereference</code>）和成员访问（<code>member access</code>），因此，迭代器对重要的便是对<code>operator-&gt;</code>和<code>operator*</code>的重载。</p><hr /><hr /><h2 id="迭代器对象"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器对象"></a> 迭代器对象</h2><h3 id="迭代器类别之-value_type"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器类别之-value_type"></a> 迭代器类别之 <code>value_type</code></h3><p><code>value_type</code>便是迭代器所指对象的类型，任何一个打算与<code>STL</code>搭配的<code>class</code>都要定义属于自己的<code>value_type</code>内嵌类型。</p><hr /><h3 id="迭代器类别之-difference_type"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器类别之-difference_type"></a> 迭代器类别之 <code>difference_type</code></h3><p><code>difference_type</code>表示两迭代器之间的距离，因此它可以用来表示一个容器的最大容量，对于连续容器而言，如<code>array</code>,<code>vector</code>，头尾之间的距离便是最大容量。针对相应类别的<code>difference_type</code>不同，由<code>C++</code>内建的<code>ptrdiff_t</code>(定义于<code>&lt;cstddef&gt;</code>头文件)作为<code>difference_type</code>。</p><hr /><h3 id="迭代器类别之-reference"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器类别之-reference"></a> 迭代器类别之 <code>reference</code></h3><p><code>reference</code>即为引用，即迭代器所指对象的指针。我们为了方便表示，可将<code>value_type &amp;</code>声明为<code>reference</code>，当然，迭代器也被分为两类：可改变所知对象内容的（<code>T&amp;</code>），和不可改变所指对象内容的（<code>const T&amp;</code>），我们可以对其进行“偏特化”设计，这会在下文“萃取器”讲到。</p><hr /><h3 id="迭代器类别之-pointer"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器类别之-pointer"></a> 迭代器类别之 <code>pointer</code></h3><p><code>pointer</code>也就是指针，即迭代器所指对象的指针。当然，与<code>reference</code>一样，会有“偏特化”设计对其进行<code>T*</code>与<code>const T*</code>进行区别。</p><hr /><h3 id="迭代器类别之-iterator_category"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器类别之-iterator_category"></a> 迭代器类别之 <code>iterator_category</code></h3><p>迭代器是我们用来操作容器中的元素的，使用根据该迭代器的移动与操作特性，迭代器可被分为五类：</p><ul><li><code>input_iterator</code>：只读，不写；单遍扫描，只能递增。</li><li><code>output_iterator</code>：只写，不读；单遍扫描，只能递增。</li><li><code>forward_iterator</code>：可读，可写；多遍扫描，只能递增。</li><li><code>bidirectional_iterator</code>：可读，可写；多遍扫描，可递增，可递减。</li><li><code>random_access_iterator</code>：可读，可写；多遍扫描，支持全部迭代器运算。</li></ul><p>此时我们可以定义五个<code>class</code>来代表这五种迭代器类型：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">input_iterator_tag</span> &#123;</span> &#125;;                                              <span class="comment">//只读迭代器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">output_iterator_tag</span> &#123;</span> &#125;;                                             <span class="comment">//只写迭代器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">forward_iterator_tag</span> :</span> <span class="keyword">public</span> input_iterator_tag &#123; &#125;;                <span class="comment">//向前迭代器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">bidirectional_iterator_tag</span> :</span> <span class="keyword">public</span> forward_iterator_tag &#123; &#125;;        <span class="comment">//双向迭代器</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">random_access_iterator_tag</span> :</span> <span class="keyword">public</span> bidirectional_iterator_tag &#123; &#125;;  <span class="comment">//随机迭代器</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>至于该迭代器类型的继承关系，在后续的<code>adcance</code>会有体会。</p><hr /><h3 id="迭代器定义"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器定义"></a> 迭代器定义</h3><p>由以上五点可以知道，<code>iterator</code>所具备的类型，所以可知<code>iterator</code>的定义如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Category</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">T</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Distance</span> =</span> std::<span class="keyword">ptrdiff_t</span>, <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Pointer</span> =</span> T*, <span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Reference</span> =</span> T&amp;&gt;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">iterator</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> Category       iterator_category;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T              value_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> Distance       difference_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T*             pointer;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T&amp;             reference;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><hr /><h2 id="萃取器"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#萃取器"></a> 萃取器</h2><h3 id="定义萃取器"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#定义萃取器"></a> 定义萃取器</h3><p>我们在前面的迭代器对象里讲到，迭代器之中有着好多的类别，不同的迭代器应该有着不同的特性，在不同的容器中的迭代器也应该有不同的特性，由此便产生了“迭代器萃取器”（<code>iterator_traits</code>）。萃取器便是为了方便提取各迭代器中各类型而产生的。</p><p>普通实现萃取一个迭代器的类型可将<code>iterator_traits</code>定义如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">I</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">iterator_traits</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">typename</span> I::iterator_category    iterator_category;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">typename</span> I::value_type           value_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">typename</span> I::difference_type      difference_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">typename</span> I::pointer              pointer;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">typename</span> I::reference            reference;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>尽管这个萃取器能将<code>iterator</code>中的各个属性提取出来，但遇到传入型的<code>pointer</code>和<code>const-to-pointer</code>（或是<code>reference</code>和<code>const-to-reference</code>）我们应该对其萃取器进行偏特化设计。</p><hr /><h3 id="萃取器的偏特化设计"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#萃取器的偏特化设计"></a> 萃取器的偏特化设计</h3><p>对原生指针<code>pointer</code>和<code>reference</code>的萃取器偏特化设计：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">T</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">iterator_traits</span>&lt;</span>T*&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> random_access_iterator_tag  iterator_category;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T                           value_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">ptrdiff_t</span>                   difference_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T*                          pointer;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T&amp;                          reference;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>对原生指针<code>const-to-pointer</code>或<code>const-to-reference</code>的萃取器偏特化设计：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">T</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="class"><span class="keyword">struct</span> <span class="title">iterator_traits</span>&lt;</span><span class="keyword">const</span> T*&gt;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> random_access_iterator_tag  iterator_category;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> T                           value_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">ptrdiff_t</span>                   difference_type;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> T*                    pointer;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> <span class="keyword">const</span> T&amp;                    reference;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><hr /><h2 id="迭代器的类型提取函数"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器的类型提取函数"></a> 迭代器的类型提取函数</h2><p>我们想要将迭代器的类型单独提取出来去使用的话，我们需要几个函数来辅助我们</p><h3 id="提取category"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#提取category"></a> 提取<code>category</code></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Iterator</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typename</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::<span class="function">iterator_category <span class="title">iterator_category</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> Iterator&amp;)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">typedef</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::iterator_category category;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="built_in">category</span>();</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="提取value_type"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#提取value_type"></a> 提取<code>value_type</code></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Iterator</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::<span class="function">value_type <span class="title">value_type</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> Iterator&amp;)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">typename</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::value_type*&gt;(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="提取difference_type"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#提取difference_type"></a> 提取<code>difference_type</code></h3><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Iterator</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typedef</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::<span class="function">difference_type <span class="title">difference_type</span><span class="params">(<span class="keyword">const</span> Iterator&amp;)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> <span class="keyword">static_cast</span>&lt;<span class="keyword">typename</span> iterator_traits&lt;Iterator&gt;::difference_type*&gt;(<span class="number">0</span>);</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><hr /><h2 id="提取迭代器间的距离"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#提取迭代器间的距离"></a> 提取迭代器间的距离</h2><p>提取距离的函数应该有两个版本实现，因为在五个迭代器类型中，针对不同的类型可以有不同的计算方法，从而产生不同的效率。</p><h3 id="逐一累计距离"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#逐一累计距离"></a> 逐一累计距离</h3><p>这一类型的距离计算只能逐一增加，即只能进行<code>i++</code>操作。</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">InputIterator</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typename</span> iterator_traits&lt;InputIterator&gt;::difference_type _distance(InputIterator first, InputIterator last, input_iterator_tag)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    iterator_traits&lt;InputIterator&gt;::difference_type n = <span class="number">0</span>;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(first != last)</span><br><span class="line">    &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        first++;</span><br><span class="line">        n++;</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> n;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="直接计算距离"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#直接计算距离"></a> 直接计算距离</h3><p>这一类型的距离计算能直接计算出其迭代器间的距离，即能进行<code>i+n</code>templa</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">RandomItertor</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">typename</span> iterator_traits&lt;RandomIterator&gt;::difference_type _distance(RandomIterator first, RandomIterator last, random_access_iterator_tag)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">return</span> last - first;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><hr /><h2 id="迭代器的前进"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#迭代器的前进"></a> 迭代器的前进</h2><p>不同迭代器的前进有所不同，如<code>forward_iterator</code>只能前进（<code>i++</code>）、<code>bidirectional_iterator</code>能前进也能后退（<code>i++</code>,<code>i--</code>）、<code>random_access_iterator</code>能随意加减任意数值（<code>i+n</code>,<code>i-n</code>等）。</p><p>所以，对不同的迭代器要有着不同的前进（<code>advance</code>）函数。</p><h3 id="向前迭代器版本"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#向前迭代器版本"></a> 向前迭代器版本</h3><p>该迭代器只能进行递增操作：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">InputIterator</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Distance</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> _advance(InputIterator&amp; i, Distance n, input_iterator_tag)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">while</span>(n--)</span><br><span class="line">        i++;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="双向迭代器版本"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#双向迭代器版本"></a> 双向迭代器版本</h3><p>该迭代器能进行递增和递减操作：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">BidirectionalIterator</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Distance</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> _advance(BidirectionalIterator&amp; i, Distance n, bidirectional_iterator_tag)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">if</span>(n &gt; <span class="number">0</span>)</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(n--)</span><br><span class="line">            i++;</span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="keyword">else</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="keyword">while</span>(n++)</span><br><span class="line">            i--</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="随机迭代器版本"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#随机迭代器版本"></a> 随机迭代器版本</h3><p>该迭代器能进行任意操作：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">RandomAccessIterator</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Distance</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">void</span> _advance(RandomAccessIterator&amp; i, Distance n, random_access_iterator_tag)</span><br><span class="line">&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    i += n;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><h3 id="向前函数"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#向前函数"></a> 向前函数</h3><p>该函数能对任意迭代器进行操作（基于以上三个迭代器版本）和迭代器类型提取函数：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">template</span> &lt;<span class="class"><span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Iterator</span>, <span class="keyword">class</span> <span class="title">Distance</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"><span class="keyword">void</span> <span class="title">advance</span><span class="params">(Iterator&amp; i, Distance n)</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="function"></span>&#123;</span><br><span class="line">    _advance(i, n, <span class="built_in">iterator_category</span>(i));</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><hr /><hr /><h2 id="总结"><a class="markdownIt-Anchor" href="#总结"></a> 总结</h2><p>由以上可知，我们可以将迭代器对象封装在一个头文件里，叫它<code>iterator.hpp</code>，为什么头文件后缀是<code>.hpp</code>，而不是<code>.h</code>，这是因为我们把类的声明与其方法定义等都放在一个文件夹内，所以叫它<code>.hpp</code>，当然，没有后缀名或者后缀名为<code>.h</code>也是可以的。</p><p>为了与<code>C++</code>标准库区分，我们把该定义放在一个<code>namespace</code>里，这里，我把它叫做<code>mystd</code>。</p><p><code>iterator.hpp</code>完整源代码如下：</p><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36<